Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:30.67,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be watching you from your shadows. {ep 37}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.13,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.32,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Evening! It's your favorite florist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.00,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Colonel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.45,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:58.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit drunk and ended up buying a lot of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:01.91,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you'd be willing to take a few off my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.96,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:14.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:18.30,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.38,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to kindly refuse the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:22.79,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I don't own a vase to put them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:27.72,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you for giving me a call. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:42.25,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he have such good timing when it comes to things like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:21.13,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,A man thought to be Scar was sighted on a mountain trail near the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.06,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,We should start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.39,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.79,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.34,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,This town, Baschool, is now a ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.90,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,It would make a great hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.70,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,How troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.90,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.53,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,If a party spots him, report back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.58,Default,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:50.51,Default,Hein,0000,0000,0000,,We'll accompany the Elric Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:51.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're coming to keep an eye on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How should we get rid of these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.60,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I just saw a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.52,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:22.55,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.66,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.82,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Did they go into that room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.42,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them, running around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to get rid of them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:44.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...too big, don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:50.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Scar and that little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:55.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't randomly show up,\Nit'll be impossible for us to find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.23,Default-alt,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.59,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:00.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.17,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She really showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.53,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.68,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.51,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you came here looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.13,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.36,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:31.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you and learn more about Eastern Alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:35.49,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! Am I dreaming? Sir Al came looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.78,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.49,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dying to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and teach us Eastern Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.74,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You brothers are feuding for my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:49.08,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not my type, Edward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.57,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.28,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.16,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.12,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.51,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that woman, Sir Alphonse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.12,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible... You have me, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No! She's just an old friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:12.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Why am I talking like a two-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:16.44,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,May, please don't run off by yourself-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.19,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.98,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:28.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.67,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.24,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.45,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare say you forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:42.27,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yoki, the great coal-mine owner of Youswell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't even think I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:49.26,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,How awful! After all those things you did to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.38,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Youswell, a mining town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:07:01.73,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I, Yoki, was a soldier and manager of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:07.24,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the town lived happily due to my efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:28.19,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And that's where the uttermost villain,\NEdward Elric, a State Alchemist, showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.24,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:11.21,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,They were working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.68,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And I, who had the mine stolen from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:24.06,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...suffered at the hands of the people who forgot what they owed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.39,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...and was given a bad name by the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:33.28,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I started many businesses in order to return to popularity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.82,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...but it all ended in failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.38,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,My investments...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.50,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...also ended in failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.05,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And my last resort...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:55.53,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,...was to ask a millionaire for a goodwill loan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:31.16,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,If only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.72,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,If only it hadn't been for those Elric Brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.95,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,And that was when I swore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:42.86,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Swore to take revenge against those two who brought me down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:48.06,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,An act of revenge far worse than death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:54.16,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to a thief like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.23,Default-alt,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm not really a thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:59.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, there's nothing between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! I need to ask you about Eastern Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.33,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How about you two listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever. It must have been hard, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.17,Default-alt,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Quit pretending like you were listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.75,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You can't find Miss Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:17.70,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... what were you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.24,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:23.25,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Two men from Charlie squad come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.30,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Major Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:30.27,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Scar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.48,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you if I find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.25,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,This place is no good either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.27,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,There's barely anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.87,Default,Jerso,0000,0000,0000,,You're Scar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.23,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kimblee would like to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.42,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.97,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you were able to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:06.06,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think the two of you can take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:10.06,Default,Zampano,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not, if we were ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.12,Default,Zampano,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If{\i0\fscx30} {\r} we were ordinary humans, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.02,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Chimeras, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.42,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned a lot since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,First, the method to create a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Second, the history of this country. And that there's something odd about the alchemy this country uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:59.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we came after this girl, seeking a possibility in Eastern Alchemy from Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.28,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less to be expected from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:06.58,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, someone realized it far before you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:10.04,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,These are the research documents he left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:15.80,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,We think these documents may hold a clue to solving the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:19.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So if we could decipher it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.31,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.55,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that, we need Scar's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.77,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.31,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,That's where Scar went!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.77,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:42.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You four hide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.18,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Scar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.42,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He's fat, but that doesn't slow him down at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:10.60,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're powerless unless you can actually touch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.07,0:13:14.31,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to be attacking from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:32.79,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,And we're also aware that you attempt to destroy the ground when things get bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:36.25,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beat you to a pulp and hand you over to Sir Kimblee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:43.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.55,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,The Elric Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.09,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:52.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, they're Kimblee's men from Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:57.95,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do anything besides watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.23,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to capture Scar-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.67,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,A monster!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.24,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that for?! We're on your sid-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall having any monsters on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How frightening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to pretend they're on our side, then eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:17.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The fat one back there has a really big mouth! He'll eat me whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.74,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,You brat! Stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.47,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Is he faster than Scar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.38,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.69,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like my limbs are made of feathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Northern automails are fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:57.18,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too cocky now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I guess my punches lost some force, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.08,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,My spit won't come off that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is slob?! That's just gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I decompose it, it's pretty much water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.02,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's cold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that for, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.97,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Ow! Stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.28,Default-alt,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to tear my skin off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:32.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How did you like my "Touching Cold Metal With Wet Hands and Getting Stuck Together" attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.07,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Quit getting in our way, Fullmetal Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.00,Default,Zan,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you on {\i1}our{\i0\fscx30} {\r} side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pig! I don't know anyone who looks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, anyone can tell you're a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you still insist that you're on our side, prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.51,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll transform back, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.72,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Zampano!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish of you to sheath\Nyour sword in front of your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.38,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.33,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to need you to take a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's in fighting shape, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get caught already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Face trial, Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.91,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy whoever gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.83,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming head-on, without thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:42.24,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Your steel arm is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:50.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's not made out of steel anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.58,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Why did you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.69,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:26.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Major Miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:37.06,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,The people at Central seem to be conducting awful experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.46,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Tie them to that pillar over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.85,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:50.24,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't please me to pass judgment on a fellow countryman, but I can't let someone like you run free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.00,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow countryman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:56.24,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Elric Brothers, we'll take care of the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:58.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Winry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.89,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go... I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How will you be fine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.89,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from him, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.42,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.86,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to him face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:31.14,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.89,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I say, it'll be only be an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:41.90,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is I killed the Rockbells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.49,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the location of the building we received a report from!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:13.00,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. We've been down here for more than twenty-four hours, which is what we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.00,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Ice Queen we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.07,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she really sealed the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.83,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural we took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:24.76,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,We groped our way here with the lanterns out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:29.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Since they insisted a monster would come if we kept the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.49,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.34,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.34,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Take these two to the infirmary. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.79,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.14,Default,Guy5,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:58.38,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to seal the exit after twenty-four hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:01.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. But, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been twenty-four hours yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:13.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Major General Armstrong told me to go by this watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:23.96,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.46,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Was the advance unit safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.91,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Just two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:34.92,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.24,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.42,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:45.43,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Winter is nice here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.35,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I only see black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.90,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,It's very plain, and I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.84,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.87,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,If you look up, there's also the color blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:03.20,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a person's heart, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.45,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,I greatly appreciate you giving us leeway this time, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:13.19,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.76,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've got some guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.30,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:43.93,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for asking this the moment of my arrival,\Nbut is there something you owe us an explanation for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:57.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All men, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:07.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.95,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:10.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:13.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell didn't you keep an eye on Winry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:17.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kimblee, the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:24:00.69,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if an encounter is accompanied by grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:03.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is still meaning in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:09.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The path to take is inscribed in feelings that come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:15.18,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:18.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 39, Daydream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:24.86,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything part of a plan devised by a superior being?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.22,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,1914
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.59,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Youswell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.95,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and pay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.45,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,your taxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.58,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't because you keep cutting our salaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.34,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver pocketwatch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.85,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,State Alchemist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.48,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.73,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy the rights to the coal mine with this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.37,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about, Mr. Alchemist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.38,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,All the gold I received from you turned into rocks!
